---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="How to play | Git Blog Play">
  <h1>How to play</h1>
  <ol class="card">
    <li>Fork the repository.</li>
    <li>Improve any markdown post in <code>/content/posts</code>.</li>
    <li>Open a pull request.</li>
    <li>Maintainers review, label, and merge.</li>
    <li>GitHub Action creates a score event and updates leaderboard files.</li>
  </ol>
</BaseLayout>
